## Key Features
- MP3 to M4B audiobook conversion
- Metadata editing (title, author, narrator, genre, year, description)
- Chapter management with timing
- Drag & drop track reordering
- Project save/restore (.audiopie.json)
- Configurable FFmpeg/FFprobe paths

## Requirements
- Node.js 18+
- FFmpeg and FFprobe in PATH or configured in settings
